caption:
New In! Mazda 787B – the first rotary-powered car to conquer Le Mans. And now? It’s yours to build. ✨

With 1796 pieces, remote-controlled drive & steering, and a fully functional four-rotor R26B engine, this 1:10 scale beast is as real as it gets.

Swing open the doors. Pop the engine cover. Admire every line of that iconic rear diffuser and spoiler.

This isn’t just a model — it’s a full-throttle tribute to racing’s loudest legend.

#buildtheunimaginable #24builds
